<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>sample</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://pro.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.10.0/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-AYmEC3Yw5cVb3ZcuHtOA93w35dYTsvhLPVnYs9eStHfGJvOvKxVfELGroGkvsg+p" crossorigin="anonymous"/>
<style>
    body{
        background-color: black;
        align-content: center;
    }
h5{
    
  padding-top: 10px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  text-align:center;
  width:100px;
  height:30px;
  background-color: white;
}
.learn{

    width:180px;
    height:300px;
    padding:40px;
    border: 0px solid;
    background-color: orange;
    font:white;
    
}

section{
       margin:136px;
        display:flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap:0px;
        width:270px;
        height:1150px;
        background-color: white;
        padding-top:20px;
        padding-left: 20px ;
        padding-right: 10px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;

    }
.left-corner{
    border-top-left-radius: 10px; 
        border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;
    border-top-right-radius: 10px;
}
.right-corner{
    border-top-left-radius: 0px; 
    border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
    border-top-right-radius: 0px;
}
@media(min-width:400px){
    section{
        display:flex;
        width:800px;
        height:375px;
        background-color: white;
        padding-top:60px;
        padding-left: 60px ;
        padding-right: 50px;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
        flex-direction: row;
        gap:0px;
        align-content: center;

    }
    .left-corner{
        border-top-left-radius: 10px; 
        border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
    border-top-right-radius: 0px;
    }
    .right-corner{
    border-top-left-radius: 0px; 
    border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
    border-top-right-radius: 10px;
}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<section>
    <div class='learn left-corner' >
        <div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius: 50%;background-color:#d28008;"> </div>
        <i class="fas fa-car-side" style="position:relative;top:-20px;right:-20px"></i>
        <h2 style="color:white;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;">SEDANS</h2>
        <p style="color:white;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:30px;"> Choose a sedan for its affordability and execellent fuel economy. Ideal for cruising in the city or on your next road trip</p>
        <h5 style="color: hsl(31, 77%, 52%);margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:30px;">Learn more</h5>
    </div>

    <div class='learn' style="background-color:hsl(184, 100%, 22%);">
        <div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius: 50%;background-color:hsl(184deg 68% 22%);"> </div>
        <i class="fas fa-car-side" style="position:relative;top:-20px;right:-20px"></i>
        <h2 style="color:white;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;">SUVS</h2>
        <p style="color:white;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:30px;"> Take an SUV for its spacious interior, power, and versatility. Perfect for your next family vacation and off-road adventures.</p>
        <h5 style="color:hsl(184, 100%, 22%);margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:30px;">Learn more</h5>
    </div>
    <div class='learn right-corner' style="background-color:hsl(179, 100%, 13%)">
        <div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius: 50%;background-color:hsl(179deg 86% 12%);"> </div>
        <i class="fas fa-car-side" style="position:relative;top:-20px;right:-20px"></i>
        <h2 style="color:white;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;">LUXURY</h2>
        <p style="color:white;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:30px;"> Cruise in the boat car brands without the bloated prices. Enjoy the enhanced comfort of a luxury rental and arrive in style.</p>
        <h5 style="color:hsl(179, 100%, 13%);margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:30px;">Learn more</h5>
    </div>

</section>
</body>
</html>
